# PAPER DISCOVERY & READING

Use methods from `/paper_related_works` and `/topic_survey`.

**Discover:** Semantic Scholar API, web search, citation chains, `/paper_related_works` logic.

**Read** via AlphaXiv (always try first):
```
WebFetch: https://alphaxiv.org/overview/{PAPER_ID}.md
WebFetch: https://alphaxiv.org/abs/{PAPER_ID}.md
```

**Store** all papers in refs.db immediately after discovery.

